  [1]
  $ pasv check --outdir="${OUTDIR}" --roi-start="${ROI_START}" --roi-end="${ROI_END}" "${ALN}" "${RESIDUES}"
  $ diff "${EXPECTED_SIGNATURES_WITH_ROI}" "${OUTDIR}/${ACTUAL_SIGNATURES}"

With ROI start.

